</div>
<div class="right-grid">
<div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/hal-aki-achievement-badges/%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E5%85%88%E9%81%94%E3%81%AF%E3%81%82%E3%82%89%E3%81%BE%E3%81%BB%E3%81%97%E3%81%8D%E3%81%93%E3%81%A8.png" width="50" alt="%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E5%85%88%E9%81%94%E3%81%AF%E3%81%82%E3%82%89%E3%81%BE%E3%81%BB%E3%81%97%E3%81%8D%E3%81%93%E3%81%A8.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong>众望所归的前辈</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>发布一篇文章</strong></span></p>
</div>
<div class="left-grid">
<div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/hal-aki-achievement-badges/%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E3%83%9F%E3%82%B9%E3%82%BF%E3%83%BC%E3%83%BB%E3%81%9D%E3%81%86%E3%81%95%E3%81%8F.png" width="50" alt="%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E3%83%9F%E3%82%B9%E3%82%BF%E3%83%BC%E3%83%BB%E3%81%9D%E3%81%86%E3%81%95%E3%81%8F.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong>创作先生</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>发布10篇以上的SCP文档</strong></span></p>
</div>
<div class="right-grid">
<div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/hal-aki-achievement-badges/%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E7%89%A9%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6%E8%80%85.png" width="50" alt="%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E7%89%A9%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6%E8%80%85.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong>物理学家</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>发布一篇评分20以上的、包含下列任一标签的SCP文档：反物理定律、反熵、电力、磁性、重力影响</strong></span></p>
</div>
<div class="left-grid">
<div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scp-jp.wdfiles.com/local--files/hal-aki-achievement-badges/%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E9%87%91%E3%83%A1%E3%83%80%E3%83%AB.png" width="50" alt="%E5%AE%9F%E7%B8%BE_%E9%87%91%E3%83%A1%E3%83%80%E3%83%AB.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong>金奖章</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>发布一篇评分50以上的文档</strong></span></p>
</div>
<div class="right-grid">
<div class="image-container floatleft"><img src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--files/achievement-badges/18.png" width="50" alt="18.png" class="image" /></div>
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong>生灵的光辉闪耀时</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:85%;"><strong>创作至少6篇20+的作品，其中至少一篇包含「<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E6%A4%8D%E7%89%A9">植物</a>」/「<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E6%A0%91%E6%9C%A8">树木</a>」/「<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E4%BB%99%E4%BA%BA%E6%8E%8C">仙人掌</a>」标签、至少三篇包含「<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E5%8A%A8%E7%89%A9">动物</a>」标签、至少一篇包含「<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E9%B8%9F%E7%B1%BB">鸟类</a>」标签、至少一篇包含「<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E5%A4%B4%E8%B6%B3%E7%B1%BB%E5%8A%A8%E7%89%A9">头足类动物</a>」标签、至少一篇包含「<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E6%97%A0%E8%84%8A%E6%A4%8E%E5%8A%A8%E7%89%A9">无脊椎动物</a>」/「<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E6%98%86%E8%99%AB">昆虫</a>」/「<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E8%8A%82%E8%82%A2%E5%8A%A8%E7%89%A9">节肢动物</a>」标签、至少一篇包含「<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E7%88%AC%E8%A1%8C%E7%B1%BB%E5%8A%A8%E7%89%A9">爬行类动物</a>」/「<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E5%BC%82%E5%85%B3%E8%8A%82%E7%9B%AE">异关节目</a>」标签、至少一篇包含「<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/system:page-tags/tag/%E9%B1%BC%E7%B1%BB">鱼类</a>」标签。</strong></span></p>
</div>
</div>
